title: 1934 Western - Gold Strike River - John Wayne - This Cowboy's Gamble: Gold or a Grave?

sources.title: 1934 Western - Gold Strike River - John Wayne - This Cowboy's Gamble: Gold or a Grave?
sources.description:
Jerry Mason (Wayne), a young Texan, and Jake Benson (George 'Gabby' Hayes'), an old rancher, become partners and strike it rich with a gold mine. But their partnership is put to the test when their new-found wealth makes them a target for jealousy and schemers.

Original title: The Lucky Texan (1934)
Written and directed by Robert N. Bradbury

Main cast:
John Wayne - Jerry Mason
Barbara Sheldon - Betty Benson
Lloyd Whitlock - Harris
George "Gabby" Hayes - Jake "Grandy" Benson
Yakima Canutt - Joe Cole
Eddie Parker - Al Miller, the sheriff's son
Gordon De Main - Williams, the banker
Earl Dwire - Sheriff Miller


Black & White version: https://youtu.be/IbkrTFerGvk
